            <p class="mt-6 mb-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              A website where I've documented all my progress from the HCI Technologies course using HTML, CSS, and JS.
            </p>
            <a href="https://hci-houwin-portfolio.netlify.app/" class="flex items-center justify-between group-hover:text-purple-500">
